Package: limeaid
Type: Package
Title: Diagnose LIME Explanations
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Katherine Goode
Maintainer: Katherine Goode <kgoode@iastate.edu>
Description: limeaid contains functions for the assessment of explanations 
             produced by the lime R package. LIME can easily be applied 
             with multiple tuning parameters, and diagnostics plots for 
             assessing the explanations are available.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
